org.omg.CORBA.portable.IDLEntity, org.omg.CORBA.portable.InvokeHandler, MTS, MTSOperations, org.omg.CORBA.Object, java.lang.Runnable, java.io.Serializable
public class FIPA_2000_IIOP_Connection
extends _MTSImplBase
implements java.lang.Runnable

FIPA_2000_IIOP_Connection is a concreat implementation of the FIPA.MTS interface that is designed to talk to zeus.actors.fipa.FIPA_2000_Server implementors. It runs in its own thread, when it recieves a message it calls the server and puts that message on a Queue. The server then dequeues the messages and deals with them as it sees fit.
